Dialogs.Dialog: 姉ヶ崎
Hmm.
What's wrong？
Well, I'm thinking about my New Year resolution. We usually forget about it soon after New Year's Day, right？
Every year, I try to come up with a resolution that I must not forget.
But then, I can't decide which resolution I should choose to be the one that I must not forget.
The resolution that you must not forget？
Any idea？
Hmm... This is difficult.
Right？ So I often have troubles deciding my resolution until spring.
Hah... I wonder how it's going to be this year.
姉ヶ崎
Hey, I've been thinking that it's weird...
What is？
Did you have to make a demon mask for Setsubun festival when you were in kindergarten？
Ah, I did.
That's the thing... Then you threw beans at the demon, right？ Like, "Demon, go away~"
Yeah. That's what we did on Setsubun.
But, the ones throwing the beans can't be the demon, right？ So why does everyone have to make a demon mask, then？
Eh？
Hey, do you think it's weird that everyone has to make a demon mask while no one becomes demon？
Well, when you say it like that, I agree.
Right？
姉ヶ崎
Hey... Do you think it's too much for a boy if he has to carry a lot of presents？
Hmm... That depends, I think.
How about you？
I think I'll be really happy with that.
Really？
Yeah, I think.
I see... That's good.
What do you mean？
No, I was talking to myself. It's nothing, so don't worry.
姉ヶ崎
Hey, do you hate sweets？
...Ah, it's this season again.
Eh？ What season？
I don't know.
Hehe. Then it's gonna be something sweet. What kinds of sweets do you like？
Hmm. I don't think I have any preference.
Many boys like dark chocolate. How about that？
Not really for me...
Geez. Can you at least give me a hint？
姉ヶ崎
It's almost Valentine's Day. Is there something you want？
Hmm... If you give me a chocolate, I'll be very happy.
You can ask for something else, too.
Something else？
Like, some desserts other than chocolate... or even some clothes, or shoes.
Hmm... But it's Valentine's Day, after all. A chocolate would be best.
Anything else besides chocolate？
A chocolate would be enough.
If you think of something else, tell me, okay？ I'll be happy to give you any presents.
姉ヶ崎
It's almost time to put the dolls on decoration. Do you feel like spring's coming soon？
Doll decoration... You mean Hinamatsuri？
Did I say something weird？
No. I just didn't get what you mean at first.
At my house, we're always busy setting up the dolls display two nights before the festival.
Hehe. We take the dolls' boxes out beforehand, but we usually leave the boxes there after we're done with the dolls.
The room will look a bit untidy for a while with all the boxes in it...
On the festival day when we decorate the doll, the room will suddenly look brilliant.
Ah, that's why you feel like spring's coming.
Yes. For me, until I see the dolls on decoration, I don't feel like winter's over yet.
By the way, it's almost White Day, but...
姉ヶ崎
It's okay. If you can be with me, that's enough already.
I don't think so.
No, it's really okay. And... Come on...
Hmm？
Besides me... do you have to give other girls return gifts, too？
Eh？
Ah, no. Never mind. Never mind.
Anyway, I know it's not a big deal, but I'll give you a return gift.
O-Okay. But, instead of a gift, I just want you to be with me. ...Just remember that, okay？
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. It's coming soon... right？
Coming soon... You mean White Day？
Geez. If you don't play dumb along with me, it's not fun.
Sorry.
Don't apologize. Instead of apologizing, you should plan for a lot of things on White Day, right？
I'm beat. If you say a lot of things, I...
Hehe. I was just joking. Just joking.
Then on White Day...
I won't be expecting anything much, so don't overdo it and don't do something unreasonable, okay？
Okay, I'll keep that in mind.
Hehe. I'll be looking forward to it. I wonder what you'll do for me.
Ah, it's almost White Day... What should I do？
姉ヶ崎
Geez, you shouldn't have asked me that, right？
Even if you say that...
Hehe. It's common sense to give me something 3 times more valuable than what I gave you. I'm looking forward to it.
Three times...？ My pocket money is probably not enough.
No, not something you buy with money. It can be something filled with your feelings... okay？
Then... I have to give you back 3 times more than your feelings？
Yes, right. And... I can accept it if you want to give it to me in installments, okay？
That's fair enough.
Hehe. I'll only charge low handling fee. And the settlement date is on the 14th, okay？
姉ヶ崎
It's already the cherry blossom season...
They are beautiful...
Did you know？ If you don't take care of cherry trees, they'll wither in no time.
They must be hard to grow.
It's just like relationships between people, don't you think？
That's why I like cherry blossoms. I like them in spring, in summer, in fall, and in winter.
I can't think of cherry blossoms in other seasons except the spring.
That's common. But it's not like cherry blossoms appear out of nowhere in spring, right？
They've always been here.
Always been here... huh？
Hehe, I'll always be here, too, as long as you need me.
姉ヶ崎
It's almost Golden Week. Do you have any plans？
None at all. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, how about you？
Me, neither. I'll probably spend my time working at a part-time job.
I should probably do that as well, then.
Ah, you don't have keep me company at work, you know？
But I'll earn money from work and be able to be with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. It's like killing two birds with one stone.
Geez... Why do you need so much money？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, how about you？
Me？ I... Well... For when we go on dates...
B-Because girls need money for a lot of things！ ...Geez.
姉ヶ崎
...Hah.
What's wrong？
You know... Come on. It's almost the sports festival, right？
Are you not good at sports？
I'm confident with my physical strength. But if I have to run or jump... ...Hah.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is somewhat melancholic too.
Urgh.
It's okay. You'll be able to do it somehow.
...But if I can't do it, I'm gonna be very frustrated.
...Ah, you're wearing the summer uniform.
姉ヶ崎
Geez... You've just noticed？
Sorry. Even now, I'm still not used to wearing the summer uniform myself.
Do you have anything else to say？
You look good in it. You look so good that I kind of feel nervous now.
Hehe. Thanks. I'll forgive you for the flattery part then.
It wasn't flattery.
How could I tell？
...You didn't really forgive me, did you？
I already forgave you. I'm just teasing you a little bit.
Hehe. Just a little bit is okay, right？
姉ヶ崎
It's almost Tanabata... What do you think about the Tanabata story？
Hikoboshi and Orihime？
Yeah. The story about the lovers' reunion is quite romantic...
But after they reunite, they'll have to be apart again. If it's not July 7th, they can't meet each other. That's very sad.
It's sad, yeah.
Well, this might sound stupid, but after we met and I got home, I always wondered when I'd be able to see you again.
Sorry for saying something weird.
It's good that we can meet each other more than once a year.
Yeah...
It's almost the summer break...
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. But shouldn't you be thinking about the final exams first？
It's too late to worry about it now.
Which means you're really confident with it, or is it totally hopeless？
Hmm, how should I answer？
Hehe. After the exams, we can start talking about the summer break, okay？
How about before the exams？
We can talk about it moderately.
So, we can talk about it？
We'll surely want to talk about it, right？ We'll be having a lot of fun during this summer.
Speaking of which, I wonder when we can start swimming in the sea.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, well...
...What's wrong？
Hmm... Don't laugh if I tell you, okay？
Okay.
Well... It's just a little bit, but... I gained some weight...
Really？ I can't really tell just by looking...
Yeah. So, it's decided！
Eh？
I'll try my best to diet in order to look good in my swimsuit！
...Don't overdo it, okay？
All right. I'll really do my best.
(She isn't listening...)
姉ヶ崎
Right, it's almost the fireworks festival.
Fireworks...？ That'll be nice.
Then... how about a yukata？
Yukata？
Boys usually like it when the girls are wearing a yukata... How about you？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ in a yukata...？ Yeah, that'll be nice.
Then maybe I should wear it to watch the fireworks.
...Should I wear one, too？
No, you can wear your usual clothes.
Just that... I want you to keep looking at me when I wear a yukata...
I-Is that so...？
...Yeah.
姉ヶ崎
Summer break has almost ended...
Yeah...
Hehe. When I spend time with you, time flies by so fast.
Time always passes by fast when you're having fun.
Do you think so, too？
Yeah.
If it's like this, our time after this will pass by very fast then...
Even so, we've already had a lot of memorable moments, right？
...Yeah, you're right.
And we'll create a lot more memorable moments from now on, right？
姉ヶ崎
It's almost the moon viewing season.
Moon viewing？ I don't usually do that at home.
Hey, when did you know that there wasn't really a rabbit on the moon？
Hmm, I can't remember.
For me, I knew since I was a little kid. There was no air and no water on the moon, so the rabbit couldn't be there.
Were you shocked？
No, I was relieved.
Relieved？
Before that, I thought it was pitiful. Because the rabbit on the moon could only eat rice cakes and couldn't have carrots.
Ah, I see. So, you thought that it couldn't eat its favorite food.
Yeah. That's why I was relieved. I was wishing there could be some carrots on the moon.
姉ヶ崎
Don't you think our school's winter uniforms look better than the summer uniforms？
Hmm, I think both of them aren't bad. And ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ looks good in both.
Geez... You said that. Anyway, you might prefer me wearing the thin summer uniform, right？
...I can't deny that.
Hehe. Shall I keep wearing the summer uniform？
But then, you'll catch a cold.
Will you be nursing me, then？
If you catch a cold, even if it's not because of the uniform, I'll surely be nursing you. I promise.
Ah, no. It's okay. You'll get a cold from me then...
...And when I have a fever, I usually act childish. That's what people tell me.
Never mind. You can just visit me if I get sick. It's so embarrassing to let you nurse me... okay？
By the way, it's almost the culture festival. What will you do, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
姉ヶ崎
I'll be helping around, but I don't have any plans for it. How about you？
Same for me.
Hehe. Then you'll be free.
Probably.
How about we go around the festival together？
Will that be good？ To just walk around without helping others.
But if there aren't many people walking around the festival, it'd look boring, right？
Right. Although I still think it's unfair to others.
It'll be okay. I don't mind if it's a little unfair as long as I can make you happy.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you aren't good at winter sports, right？
姉ヶ崎
Like, skating or skiing？
If you don't like them, you must tell me, okay？ I don't want to force you to come with me.
No. As long as I can be with you, it doesn't matter where we go.
But, will you be okay？
Well... I can ski. Just a little bit though.
I see.
My grandma's hometown has lots of snow. That's why I skied a little bit when I was a kid.
Eh？ Then we can go skiing together this winter, right？
Yeah. We'll be making a big snowman together, okay？
(...How about skiing？)
It's almost Christmas...
姉ヶ崎
Hot Christmas...
Eh？
Ah, well... I saw it on TV. It's cold to be alone on Christmas, but if you have someone with you, it'll be warm.
So, they called it "Hot Christmas," huh？
Yeah. I've always felt warm ever since I met you.
I feel the same way, too, of course.
I'll always make you feel warm, so you have to do the same for me, okay？
We're gonna stay in a suite room in a hotel, right？
姉ヶ崎
Oh yeah. We'll have a night cruise in a helicopter, too.
Huh？
Oh yeah. We'll have a night cruise in a helicopter, too.
Excuse me...
Hehe. I was just joking, of course.
Joking？
My ideal Christmas is that we can spend our peaceful time together, anywhere, just the two of us.
A present might be nice, but just being able to be with you is more than enough for me.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... Don't frighten me.
Hehe, sorry. I just felt like teasing you a bit.
It's almost Christmas...
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. Do you think it's cruel if you have to be alone during this season？
No. Why？
In Japan, it's another occasion for lovers besides Valentine's, right？
Well, you're right.
That's why I had always thought of it as a cruel season.
How about now？ Do you still feel the same？
No. Because I already have you.
Yeah. Me, too. It feels so warm to be with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Hehe. This Christmas, this big sister will make you feel even warmer▼
姉ヶ崎
This year will end soon...
Yeah, so fast...
What was the most important thing that happened to you this year？
Eh？ Me？
Our first date？
Our first kiss？
What was it？
Of course, it was our first date.
...Right. I still can't believe you said "Okay" to me back then.
I always felt depressed and thought that it would end up as my unrequited love...
You thought it'd end up like that？
Yeah. That's why I was surprised because what I thought would end turned out to be a new start.
I see.
...Please take care of me next year, too.
Same here. Please take care of me.
Since we started dating, it's that thing... I mean, our first kiss.
Ah, yeah... It's the same to me. It was really mysterious...
Mysterious？
Because it was just that... The moment our lips touched, I felt like I had known you ever since a long, long time ago.
Me, too！ Why was that？
I don't really know, but... it was such a pleasant feeling.
Yeah... It was a special moment.
A special moment for just the two of us...
...Yeah.
Well, what was it？
Hmm... It must be... Come on, that one.
That one？
You really don't know？
I don't know. Sorry.
Geez... Idiot.
姉ヶ崎
This year has almost ended...
Many things happened this year, huh？
Yeah. It'd be nice if we can still be this way next year...
Will you still be with me？
I will. And we'll talk about what happened in the past year, like this.
I wonder if there will be a lot of things to talk about.
There will be, I'm sure.
Yeah, I think so.
Let's do a lot of things together next year, okay？ Can you promise？
It's gradually getting warm, huh？
姉ヶ崎
Hehehe. Spring is coming, so it's natural.
Natural, huh？
Don't keep your habit of oversleeping even in spring, okay？
I'll be fine, I'll be fine.
There are people who always get sleepy in spring.
I'm really okay.
Hehe. It's a nice season to take an afternoon nap. I can let you sleep on my lap.
In that case, I'd like to do that even when I'm not sleepy.
Hehe, wait until later then.
(Until later, huh...？)
姉ヶ崎
*yawn*...
Are you sleepy？
Yeah, a little bit... Maybe because it's spring.
Shall we rest a bit？
No, I'm not that sleepy. How should I say this...？ The weather is just so warm that I feel relaxed.
Because it's spring, right？
Hehe, and because you're near me, I think.
Me？
Yeah... To me, you're like the sunny spot for a cat, you know？
You mean a place where you can feel at peace？
Yeah... I hope you feel the same way with me, too.
姉ヶ崎
It's getting warmer and warmer, huh？
Summer is coming soon.
Yeah. Ah, do you want to take off your jacket？ Today's quite warm...
I'm fine. And how about you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Is it too hot？
I'm okay for now. But if I'm directly under the sun, I...
Ah, it's not about the heat. I just haven't applied any sunblock today, so I was a little worried.
Is your skin sensitive？
Not that it's sensitive, but strong sunlight isn't good for my skin. My skin is aging, you know？
But your skin still looks very nice.
Hey... I was just joking. Can you take it less seriously...？
Today's really hot...
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, but if you train your mind to... something, even the fire will feel cool, right？
Train your mind to... something？ What's that missing word？
The word slipped my mind.
Hmm... I think it starts with a "t."
Train your mind to t... transparent？
Transparent？
Aaah, that's not right. T... T... Tree？ Tree something？
Tree？
Anyway, I heard that if we eat hot noodle soup on a hot day, it would feel refreshing. Do you think it's true？
I don't know.
I wonder if it's true.
.......Somehow, our brains aren't working today, huh？
姉ヶ崎
Do you think it's getting chilly in the morning and evening lately？
Fall is approaching, huh？
But it still doesn't feel like fall at all.
Maybe it hasn't arrived yet.
Hehe. By the way, what do you think when you talk about fall？
Well... Leaves changing colors, I think？
Not just that... People usually say "Fall is for reading" or "Fall is for sports" or something like that.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, how about you？
Of course, fall is for romance. It gets cold during fall, so it's natural to link arms with each other, right？
(I don't mind doing that even if it's warm...)
姉ヶ崎
Hey, is there anything you want to eat？
Something I want to eat？ I'm not really hungry right now, though.
Geez, I didn't mean that. Come on. There is a lot of delicious food that's only available in fall, right？
Ah, people say "Fall is the season for a good appetite," right？
Yeah. So, is there anything？
Hmm... When I'm with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, anything I eat becomes very delicious.
Geez... That makes me happy, but now I can't decide what to do.
hat's the matter？
I want to go eat something with you... Or maybe cook something for you.
h, can I look forward to it？
Hehe. I don't know▼
(Urgh. She really enjoys teasing me...)
Urgh... I'm sure winter is coming soon.
姉ヶ崎
Are you cold？
I'm okay. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, how about you？
Me？ I'm okay with cold weather. But are you sure you're okay？
Hehe. I'm good with cold weather.
Ah, okay. Winter is the season I like most. It makes me feel calm.
And we'll have long holidays on New Year's, right？
I'm usually busy around that time and I'm not good at doing things in a hurry.
Maybe I should just relax with you this year.
Urgh. It's so cold today.
姉ヶ崎
Are you not good with cold weather？ I have this disposable hand warmer. You wanna use it？
Thanks, but I'm okay.
Geez. You should wear something thicker than this.
Right. I'll be careful.
It'd be bad if you caught a cold.
I'm okay.
...Come on. Use this hand warmer.
But then ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ will...
I'll be okay. I'm not cold. Just listen to this big sister for once.
Okay, thank you.
Geez... It's okay to behave like a spoiled child sometimes, all right？
